ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc2b873f056cd4595758a27604bf40b84220e20","tid":86293,"uid":76870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係大阪時晚晚飛田+松島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果到有咩好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9459db5dcf6b977434ed8aec7993f96b72a9350b","tid":86293,"uid":10626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貓車幾好, 郊區坐火車感覺好正. <br />\n但隻貓放咗係個玻璃櫃入面. 重差過去寵物店睇貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁慘"}]}